measures.expression:
Calculate(
    'Volume Targets'[Volume Target], 
    FILTER('Product', 'Product'[Liquid Segment] = "BEER SEGMENT"),
    FILTER(Geography, Geography[Sales Rep Classification] = "Prairies-AB-Retail-Core + Craft" )
)

measures.name: _Volume Target
measures.expression:
CALCULATE (
    SUM ( 'Volume Targets'[TGT_SLS_HL] ),
    TREATAS (
        VALUES ( 'Geography'[sls_terr_code] ),
        'Volume Targets'[SLS_TERR_CODE]
    ),
    TREATAS(
        VALUES(brand
)))

measures.name: _QTD_Dist_Actuals_OFF_P
measures.expression:
CALCULATE (
    COUNTROWS (
        SUMMARIZE (
            'Distribution Actuals',
            'Distribution Actuals'[CNSMR_PROD_CODE],
            'Distribution Actuals'[POC_SK]
        )
    ),
    'Distribution Actuals'[PREM_NAME] = "OFF",
    'Distribution Actuals'[Distribution Indicator] = True,
    'Distribution Actuals'[Active Distribution Indicator] = True
)

measures.name: _QTD_Dist_Actuals_OP_Draught
measures.expression:
CALCULATE (
        COUNTROWS (
            SUMMARIZE (
                'Distribution Actuals',
                'Distribution Actuals'[SLBL_BRD_CODE],
                'Distribution Actuals'[PKG_CLS_CODE],
                'Distribution Actuals'[POC_SK]
            )
        ),
        'Distribution Actuals'[PREM_NAME] = "ON",
		'Product'[Package Class] = "DRAUGHT",
        'Distribution Actuals'[Distribution Indicator] = True,
        'Distribution Actuals'[Active Distribution Indicator] = True
    )

measures.name: _QTD_Dist_Actuals_OP_Package
measures.expression:
